{"tid":1424923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚］CCTVB現場位置","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:48:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T02:15:22.000Z","uid":15772,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"63539840e60bd654bcd4389939fdfa882dbf9a45","tid":1424923,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:48:26.000Z","msg":"大家都知CCTVB除咗選擇性報導、偏幫小強同林奠之外<br />\n仲成日偷影我地班手足<br />\n又扮其他報館既人<br />\n鼠入人群中間影手足除罩樣<br />\n元朗個次仲入埋車箱偷影<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得可以開個TG Channel：<br />\n&bull; 第一手報cctvb即時位置<br />\n&bull; 附上現場cctvb既容貌俾手足參考<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自問唔熟識點處理資訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋舊磚希望有能者可以考慮下呢個方法去實行<br />\n<br />\n大家都集思廣益下點幫到手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"10e88352b7157a11328de205987a9b3176e427b2","tid":1424923,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:48:41.000Z","msg":"自推10連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27735497673cfb3a1532d8c441a75f3784165acd","tid":1424923,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:48:51.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"fbce8f9f2e8b681cc8850f6e9092c289c1ba2a3e","tid":1424923,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:49:01.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8760c90101f146f08a2b810d24848ad89a1f11a3","tid":1424923,"uid":15772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a0e17d01c0d8f7e041c482f5b6ead2451647b130","tid":1424923,"uid":1315,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0